resumes.text: Experienced software engineer skilled in JavaScript, Node.js, and cloud deployment. Developed scalable APIs, improved system performance, and collaborated with cross-functional teams to deliver high-impact products.

Dedicated medical doctor with experience in patient diagnosis, emergency care, and treatment planning. Skilled in maintaining patient records, collaborating with specialists, and ensuring high-quality healthcare services.
